  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "639894f488f48f001dd978b9",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 48",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b0",
      "text": "from [第一クールのクオリアさん下書き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b1",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 48",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b3",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b4",
      "text": "正義の名の下に暴力を繰り返す人がいるのは、その人たちが暴力によって新しい正義を作り出そうとしているからです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b5",
      "text": "もしその新しい正義が文明の進歩に好ましいのであれば、あなたも暴力に参加すると良い。好ましくないのであれば、その人たちをより強い暴力で無効化すると良い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b7",
      "text": "Hello, clever Homo sapiens! It's day 48.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8b9",
      "text": "The reason some people repeat violence in the name of justice is that they are trying to create a new justice through violence.(1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8ba",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/289cc484b74159828b3a2e8bd5103818]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8bc",
      "text": "If that new justice is favorable to the progress of civilization, then you can join in the violence. If it is not favorable, then you can disable those people with stronger violence.(2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8bd",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/cf586e1e41b216af44a9a13d60ae73df]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8be",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c0",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/amemy12963/status/1600413688493936641 @amemy12963]: @Qualia_san 地球では、災害が起こると日用品の買い占めが往々にして発生します。このような状況下では、ルールを守った者が相対的に損をします。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c1",
      "text": ">クオリアさんの星ではどんな行動が適切とされていますか。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c2",
      "text": "\t>[https://twitter.com/amemy12963/status/1600415619178168320?s=20&t=JnEX50iGiDE-QdsW7Ik_vw @amemy12963]: ちなみに、僕はこう考えています",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c3",
      "text": " >・まずは備蓄する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c4",
      "text": " >・生きるための不足分は多少ルールを破ってでも手に入れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c5",
      "text": " >・必要以上に入手しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c6",
      "text": " >・余っているものは他人に分配する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c7",
      "text": " >ルールは安定した人間関係があって機能するもので、お互いに信頼できない状況ではまさにサバイバルなのかなと思っています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c8",
      "text": " 「ルールを守った方が損」なルールを作って、それに他人が従うと思っているホモサピエンスは愚かです。ルールを破った方が得ならば当然ルールを破るホモサピエンスが現れる。これは現実をきちんと観察すれば明らかなことです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8c9",
      "text": " なのでこのケースではどういう行動が理想で、どういう行動を抑制したいのかを明確にし、それを実効力のあるシステムで強制すべきです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8ca",
      "text": " 例えば多くの人が必要なものを少数の人が買い占めて、それを転売することによって利益を得ようとする行為を抑制したいとしましょう。まずは転売品の販売と購入と仲介を違法化しましょう。高い罰金を掛けたり、刑務所に入れたりすれば良い。盗品の売買に関しては同様の法律がある国も多い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8cb",
      "text": " そして、警察が情報提供窓口を作り、有益な情報を提供した人に褒賞を出しましょう。社会に有益なことをできなくてフラストレーションを溜めている暇なホモサピエンスに、公的に正義の鉄槌を与えるのです。喜んで振り回してくれるでしょう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8cc",
      "text": " おっと、質問に答えていませんでした。クオリアさんの星では、必要以上に物を買い占めたら、盛んな情報共有によって、その「必要以上に物を買い占めた」という情報がありとあらゆる相手に知られます。悪いことをするとその後の生活に支障があるので、悪いことをする人はほとんどいません。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8ce",
      "text": "Q: Often when there is a disaster on earth, commodities are bought up. Under these circumstances, those who follow the rules will suffer a relative loss. What kind of behavior is considered appropriate on Qualia-san's planet? (1/6)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8cf",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/3cbdd2760ef82126ba30a3c921ff5e0b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d1",
      "text": "A: It is stupid to make rules that will cause you to lose money if you follow them and expect others to follow them. If it is more profitable to break the rules, then of course there will be Homo sapiens who break the rules. This is obvious if we observe reality properly. (2/6)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d2",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/27005eb01f4b19f0696fbfb225a80afd]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d4",
      "text": "Therefore, in this case, it is necessary to clarify what kind of behavior is ideal and what kind of behavior we want to discourage, and to enforce it with an effective system. (3/6)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d6",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b70b96b9d0baa493f11b08738b1672d2]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d8",
      "text": "Suppose we want to stop buying up items that many people need and then resell them for a profit. First, make it illegal to sell or broker resale goods. You can impose high fines or even jail them.  Many countries have similar laws regarding the sale of stolen goods. (4/6)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8d9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/920c15ecc460d53fcf9b842c38a0b7f7]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8dc",
      "text": "Then, we would have the police make a tip line and offer a reward to anyone who provides useful information. There are a lot of homo sapiens out there who are bored with being of no use to society. Let's give them some public justice. They will be happy to swing it around. (5/6)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8dd",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/90561c8e40dcbbc47d2e419537024d5a]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8df",
      "text": "Oops, I didn't answer your question. On my planet, when someone buys more stuff than they need, that information is known to everyone through active information sharing. Few people do bad things because doing bad things will get them in trouble for the rest of their lives. (6/6)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8e0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/63faf818b344f8a61cc381536ccc6377]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670943989,
      "updated": 1670943989
    },
    {
      "id": "639894f4aff09e0000ebc8e1",
